name: Baba Siddique
summary: A prominent figure in Indian society, Baba Siddique met an untimely end when he was shot dead in Mumbai. Siddique had a long and distinguished career, rising from humble beginnings in the Congress party to become a respected NCP leader and former Maharashtra minister. Notable for facilitating the reconciliation of Bollywood superstars Shah Rukh Khan and Salman Khan following their infamous altercation at Katrina Kaif's birthday party, Siddique was also the subject of police investigation regarding his involvement in the Lawrence Bishnoi gang.
